      • editThisAndFuture

                                                    java.util.Collection<I> instances)
        Description copied from class: VComponentBase

        Changing this and future instances in VComponent is done by ending the previous VComponent with a UNTIL date or date/time and starting a new VComponent from the selected instance. EXDATE, RDATE and RECURRENCES are split between both VComponents. vEventNew has new settings, vEvent has former settings.

      • streamLimitedByRange

        public java.util.stream.Stream<java.time.temporal.Temporal> streamLimitedByRange()
        Description copied from interface: VComponent

        Produces a stream of start dates or date/times by calling VComponent.stream(Temporal) using VComponent.getStartRange() as the temporal parameter, minus the duration if the VComponent has one. This stream is used by VComponent.makeInstances() to produce the displayed instances of the recurrence set.
